The proper pronunciation is more or less "vest-Fall-ya"  with the emphasis 
on Fall.  That's how a German would pronounce it.  In English-speaking 
countries, it's whatever floats-yer-boat since we don't adhere to many of 
the German-language pronunciation rules.

-David

